00:20:38.040 --> 00:20:39.610
It doesn't have to
be a work of art.

00:20:39.610 --> 00:20:43.520
Stick figures work.

00:20:43.520 --> 00:20:46.130
Focus on details that matter.

00:20:46.130 --> 00:20:49.050
We don't draw a
lot of backgrounds.

00:20:49.050 --> 00:20:52.970
We just draw the bare
minimum of elements

00:20:52.970 --> 00:20:56.120
that will get across the
intention of the scene

00:20:56.120 --> 00:20:57.310
or the shot, rather.

00:20:59.860 --> 00:21:02.580
