revise the script as needed.

00:24:40.760 --> 00:24:42.970
Sometimes a great visual
idea doesn't line up

00:24:42.970 --> 00:24:43.640
with the script.

00:24:43.640 --> 00:24:47.130
Focus on visual story, not
adherence to your script.

00:24:47.130 --> 00:24:49.810
