01:19:11.050 --> 01:19:14.410
But I'm also lit
a lot more flat.

01:19:14.410 --> 01:19:17.400
I actually think
that the footage

01:19:17.400 --> 01:19:20.450
that we had before-- it looks
a lot better, like the lighting

01:19:20.450 --> 01:19:21.990
is a lot more flattering.

01:19:21.990 --> 01:19:24.700
But it's a lot more
formal and traditional.

01:19:24.700 --> 01:19:27.550
And it's hard to know
how much that jumps out

01:19:27.550 --> 01:19:29.400
in the context of the
rest of your video

01:19:29.400 --> 01:19:30.860
until you line up
all these stills

01:19:30.860 --> 01:19:33.039
and you sort of
storyboard this way.

01:19:33.039 --> 01:19:34.830
So we haven't actually
finished this video.

01:19:34.830 --> 01:19:36.540
I'm in the process right now.

01:19:36.540 --> 01:19:39.320
Like, this is exactly
