01:19:39.320 --> 01:19:41.060
I thought I would
show it to you today

01:19:41.060 --> 01:19:42.893
since we've been talking
about storyboarding

01:19:42.893 --> 01:19:44.570
to show how you
can do it not just

01:19:44.570 --> 01:19:47.580
in pre-production, but also
after you've shot material.

01:19:50.910 --> 01:19:54.419
So we have about 20
minutes left in class.

01:19:54.419 --> 01:19:56.210
I thought that it would
